        <h1>Summertime Mango Drink</h1>
        <img src="images/mango-drink.jpeg" alt="Picture of a pitcher of a mango drink" style="width: 250px; height: 250px;">
        <h3><em>A taste of summer</em></h3>
        <h4>Quick and easy to make</h4>
    </div>
    <div>
        <h2>Ingredients</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>2 mangoes, cut into cubes</li>
            <li>1 cup ice cubes</li>
            <li>1 teaspoon vanilla extract</li>
            <li>1 tablespoon white sugar</li>
            <li>1 ⅔ cups milke</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
        <h2>Directions</h2>
        <h3>Step 1</h3>
        <p>Combine mangoes, ice cubes, vanilla extract, and sugar in a blender; pour in milk. Blend until liquefied.</p>
    </div>
